net.amoebaman.utils.chat
Class Scheme

java.lang.Object
  net.amoebaman.utils.chat.Scheme

public class Scheme
extends java.lang.Object

Defines color schemes that can be used in conjuction with the formatting methods. Ideally these can be changed at will, and have all server messages change correspondingly.

Author:
AmoebaMan
